#help.cost_cost_life
  %h2 Typical life
  
  %p This field is optional. Use it to record the typical lifespan (if any) reported for this technology in this source.
  
  %p If there is no data, leave it blank.
  
  %p The economic and physical life are assumed to be the same. If there is a difference, please note it in the notes lower on the page.
  
  %p The life should be given in years, or ranges of years:
  %ul
    %li= update_life_to '10 years'
    %li= update_life_to '15 years'
    %li= update_life_to '20 years'
    %li= update_life_to '30 years'
    %li= update_life_to '40 years'
    
  %ul
    %li= update_life_to '5-10 years'
    %li= update_life_to '10-20 years'
    %li= update_life_to '40-60 years'